Class XMLGridImporter

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.dragondelve.customdriversutil.model.xml.XMLGridImporter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GridImporter

    public class XMLGridImporter
extends java.lang.Object
implements GridImporter
    Responsible for the conversion between AMS2 XML Custom Driver storage method and this program's data model. AMS2 XML representation of the custom AI drivers can be found here: Reiza Studios Forum

      • importFromFile

        public Grid importFromFile(java.io.File file)
        Imports a grid from a given File. If the File contains a valid XML formatted with AMS2 XML representation of Custom AI it will return a Grid. This will not set the correct Class for the grid. This should be handled elsewhere.
        Specified by:
        importFromFile in interface GridImporter
        Parameters:
        file - An XML file formatted with AMS2 XML representation of Custom AI.
        Returns:
        New instance of a Grid from the source, or null if the import has failed.

      • importWithVehicleClass

        public Grid importWithVehicleClass(java.io.File file,
                                   VehicleClassLibrary library)
        Imports a grid from a given File and generates a new VehicleClass if a vehicle class is not present in the given VehicleClassLibrary. This will set the VehicleClass of Grid.
        Specified by:
        importWithVehicleClass in interface GridImporter
        Parameters:
        file - a file that contains the Grid formatted to XML.
        library - Vehicle Class Library that is meant to contain the newly loaded VehicleClass.
        Returns:
        New instance of a Grid from the source, or null if the import has failed.
